message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CV", "cs.CL", "cs.AI", "cs.LG", and "cs.IR". This is because the paper deals with visual question answering, which involves computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
